OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772597016
OL,3,CGovernment charters flight from Oman
OL,4,Con Wednesday evening
OL,6,FA Government charter flight will be
OL,7,Favailable on Wednesday evening for
OL,8,FBritish nationals wanting to leave
OL,9,FOman amid the conflict in the region.
OL,11,FThe Foreign Office said the flight
OL,12,Fwill depart the country's capital,
OL,13,FMuscat, at 7pm and is available for
OL,14,FBritish nationals, their partners and
OL,15,Fchildren under 18 with a valid travel
OL,16,Fdocument.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
