OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772597016
OL,3,CGovernment charters flight from Oman
OL,4,Con Wednesday evening
OL,6,FIt comes as Sir Keir Starmer will face
OL,7,Fquestions in the Commons over his
OL,8,Fdecisions on the unfolding Iran
OL,9,Fconflict, after Donald Trump unleashed
OL,10,Ffresh criticism of the Prime Minister.
OL,12,FAccording to the Foreign Office,
OL,13,Fpriority for the evacuation flight
OL,14,Fwill be given to the most vulnerable
OL,15,Fand they will contact British
OL,16,Fnationals in Oman. Anyone who
OL,17,Fregistered their presence in the
OL,18,FUnited Arab Emirates (UAE) and are now
OL,19,Fin Oman is asked to register for a
OL,20,Fplace on a flight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772597016
OL,3,CGovernment charters flight from Oman
OL,4,Con Wednesday evening
OL,6,FThe department asked people not to
OL,7,Ftravel to Muscat International Airport
OL,8,Fin Oman unless they are contacted by
OL,9,Fofficials, while dependents who are
OL,10,Fnot British nationals will require a
OL,11,Fvalid visa or permission to enter or
OL,12,Fremain granted for more than three
OL,13,Fmonths.
OL,15,FSome 130,000 Britons have registered
OL,16,Ftheir presence in the Middle East, as
OL,17,Fthe Foreign Office said it was working
OL,18,Fwith airlines on more routes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
