FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772597016
OL,3,CGovernment charters flight from Oman
OL,4,Con Wednesday evening
OL,6,FThe US president on Tuesday said Sir
OL,7,FKeir was "not Winston Churchill" in
OL,8,Fhis latest rebuke of the Prime
OL,9,FMinister, who did not allow American
OL,10,Fplanes to launch their initial strikes
OL,11,Fagainst Tehran from British bases.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister meanwhile announced
OL,14,FBritain would send HMS Dragon, one of
OL,15,Fthe Royal Navy's six Type 45 air
OL,16,Fdefence destroyers, to defend Cyprus
OL,17,Fafter RAF Akrotiri was hit by a drone.
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772597016
OL,3,CGovernment charters flight from Oman
OL,4,Con Wednesday evening
OL,6,FThe war between Iran and the USA, now
OL,7,Fin its fifth day, will likely dominate
OL,8,Fthe agenda when Sir Keir enters the
OL,9,FCommons at noon on Wednesday for Prime
OL,10,FMinister's Questions.
OL,12,FMr Trump has said he is "not happy"
OL,13,Fwith the UK after it did not initially
OL,14,Fallow the US to use its bases for
OL,15,Fstrikes on Iran, later adding in the
OL,16,FOval Office: "This is not Winston
OL,17,FChurchill that we're dealing with."
OL,19,FDowning Street has insisted the US
OL,20,Fremains a "staunch" ally despite the
OL,21,Frepeated broadsides from Mr Trump.
OL,26,@tD@YOUtD@cO]xD@NOUyD@cO]|D@KOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772597016
OL,3,CGovernment charters flight from Oman
OL,4,Con Wednesday evening
OL,6,FSir Keir decided on Sunday that UK
OL,7,Fbases, including the joint UK-US Diego
OL,8,FGarcia site in the Chagos Islands and
OL,9,FRAF Fairford in Gloucestershire, could
OL,10,Fbe used in the conflict, but only so
OL,11,Fthe US can strike defensively to
OL,12,Fprotect countries being targeted by
OL,13,FTehran.
OL,15,FHMS Dragon is being readied to depart
OL,16,Ffor the Mediterranean and will be
OL,17,Faccompanied by two Wildcat helicopters
OL,18,Fequipped with so-called "drone
OL,19,Fbusting" Martlet missiles, so it can
OL,20,Fprotect Britain's bases in Cyprus.
OL,26,@zD@YOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
