CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772597016
OL,3,CGovernment charters flight from Oman
OL,4,Con Wednesday evening
OL,6,FThe warship, which is emblazoned with
OL,7,Fthe Welsh red dragon on its prow, was
OL,8,Fpictured on Tuesday night at the Upper
OL,9,FHarbour Ammunition Facility (UHAF) in
OL,10,FPortsmouth harbour.
OL,12,FElsewhere, the UK Maritime Trade
OL,13,FOperations Centre (UKMTO) said a
OL,14,Fvessel had been struck by a projectile
OL,15,Foff the coast of Fujairah in the UAE.
OL,17,FIt said in a statement early on
OL,18,FWednesday: "UKMTO has received a
OL,19,Freport of an incident 7NM east of
OL,20,FFujairah, United Arab Emirates.
OL,26,@zD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
