FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772597016
OL,3,CGovernment charters flight from Oman
OL,4,Con Wednesday evening
OL,6,F"The Master reported the vessel being
OL,7,Fstruck by an unknown projectile
OL,8,Fcausing damage to the steel plating.
OL,9,FThere has been no fire or water
OL,10,Fintake. All crew reported safe.
OL,12,F"Authorities are investigating.
OL,13,FVessels are advised to transit with
OL,14,Fcaution and report any suspicious
OL,15,Factivity to UKMTO."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@SO]
